    ${
      shssi.1 $e |- H e. SH $.
      $( A closed subspace of a Hilbert space is a subset of Hilbert space. $)
      shssi $p |- H (_ H~ $=
        ( csh wcel chil wss shss ax-mp ) ACDAEFBAGH $.
        $( [6-Oct-1999] $)

      $( A member of a subspace of a Hilbert space is a vector. $)
